{
  "stem": "22750.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she lived with me in the ghetto in the hole, in the foxhole where I was at night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My life took years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's a long history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I start to talk to you, and you ask me a question-- came another thing in my mind, which I didn't mention at  the time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know if it's necessary or not necessary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I couldn't say all the details, when-- when I-- when I was hiding already, I came to the-- I don't know if you asked me this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What do you ask me now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this I-- yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I told you, I mentioned-- I had already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working on my farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was another Jew from our little city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Judenrat from our little city to Mlynow because Mlynow was the bigger little city of the two cities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mentioned its name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they picked him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then somehow somebody there-- I couldn't tell you exactly took him off-- didn't like him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was from a bigger city, educated man, intelligent man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't like him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took it off him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they picked me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or somebody gave the name, mine or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I had a sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She survived with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she walked by an officer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she asked an officer, a German officer already-- told him about my brother has a field.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he works in a field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, they picked him to go with the Judenrat to take him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She thought she will have some explanation from him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then he answered here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Your brother was chosen in German is going to-- because he doesn't want to do the job for the Wermacht at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Wermacht mean-- and I had a message.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
